Stay in the heart of Mumbai – Excellent location – show map

One of our best sellers in Mumbai! Located in Mumbai, within a 5-minute walk of Gateway of India and 1,650 feet of Colaba Causeway, Backpacker Panda Colaba features accommodations with free WiFi. Among the various facilities are a terrace and a shared lounge.

Prince of Wales Museum is a 9-minute walk from the hostel and Rajabai Clock Tower is a 13-minute walk away.

You can play darts at the hostel. Speaking English and Hindi at the reception, staff will be happy to provide guests with practical advice on the area.

Crawford Market is 1.9 mi from Backpacker Panda Colaba. The nearest airport is Chhatrapati Shivaji International Mumbai Airport, 13 mi from the property.

Couples in particular like the location – they rated it 9.4 for a two-person trip.

Please note that a link for payment would be sent for long stays/peak period/group bookings requesting for payment of the balance amount in advance.

Guests having an ID proof with a residence address of Mumbai will not permitted to check in.

Please note that at check-in, all guests above the age of 18 must present a valid proof of identification and of on-going travel.

Payment before arrival via bank transfer is required. The property will contact you after you book to provide instructions.

If you are a local resident of the city, you will not be permitted to stay at the hostel.

Guests are required to show a photo ID and credit card upon check-in. Please note that all Special Requests are subject to availability and additional charges may apply.
